hu.trigary.iodine.api.gui

Class IodineColor

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.trigary.iodine.api.gui.IodineColor

  • public final class IodineColor
extends java.lang.Object
    An immutable class representing an ARGB color. Since it is immutable, the setter methods return a new instance. The components' values range from 0x00 to 0xFF (both inclusive). An alpha channel value of 0xFF stands for full opacity (no transparency).
